Params: {3: 'The final bionic was vaporized before you, and Lucia put her blade away.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'The data you collected on Amberia from the battle just now... Was heavily fragmented and disorderly.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: '"Dreams" often don\'t conform to normal logic.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'If you integrate the memory fragments, you may be able to piece together the whole picture.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "Even if we can't see the whole picture, it's still unpleasant enough as is. Those poor people...", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Lee suddenly stopped talking in an attempt to calm down.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "Who doesn't want to wake up from this awful nightmare?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "As Asimov said, let's put an end to the nightmare, Commandant.", 4: '1'}
